          "text": "御弟驾到，孤家未曾远迎，面前恕罪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱元璋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢，小弟来得卤莽，皇兄海涵。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘福通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "岂敢。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱元璋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "皇兄见召，必有所为。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘福通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "备得酒宴，要与御弟痛饮。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱元璋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "到此就要叨扰。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘福通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "看宴。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖吹打〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘福通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "朱元璋",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘福通",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，舞剑上来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吴通耍剑，刺朱元璋，吴桢踢吴通。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴桢",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大胆！"
        },
        {
          "character": "吴桢",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "小番儿行事太狂妄，\n擅敢在酒宴前刺杀君王。\n杀了那刘福通再做商量。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（吴桢砍刘福通，众人同拦，吴桢拉朱元璋同下，众人同追下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
